            <abstract id="ref2" label="Abstract">This collection contains original artwork, sketches, sketchbooks, correspondence, articles, and paper dolls by Mary Greenough Means, a children's book illustrator. The Means family is associated with an historic Means house in Amherst, NH.</abstract>
