        <scopecontent id="ref7">
            <head>Scope and Content</head>
            <p>This collection contains original art, manuscripts and research materials for 
                <title render="italic">The Big Fish </title>, published in 1959 by 
                <corpname>Boston, Little, Brown </corpname>. It also includes sketches, sketchbooks, correspondence, articles, and paper dolls. The sets of paper dolls are mounted and framed.</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <arrangement id="ref8">
            <head>Arrangement</head>
            <p>The materials have been arranged to reflect the development of the story from idea to published book.</p>
